---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import Heading from "../components/Heading.astro"
import PostBody from "../components/PostBody.astro"

import {
  ORG_NAME,
  ORG_STREET,
  ORG_CITY,
  ORG_STATE_ABBR,
  ORG_POSTAL_CODE,
  ORG_COUNTRY,
  ORG_PHONE,
} from "../const"

const title = `DDEV Foundation`
const description = `Learn about the DDEV Foundation, a Colorado, USA 501(c)(3) nonprofit corporation that develops and maintains DDEV, the local development environment tool.`
---

<Layout
  title={title}
  description={description}
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-24">
    <Heading title={`DDEV Foundation`} />
    <div class="px-6 lg:px-0">
      <PostBody>
        <article>
          <section class="mb-8">
            <p>
              The DDEV Foundation, a Colorado (USA) nonprofit corporation, is the developer of <a href="https://ddev.com" rel="noopener">DDEV</a>. It was formerly named the Localdev Foundation. It serves as the fiscal entity for the project and owns the bank account, etc. For more, see <a href="/about">About DDEV</a>.
            </p>
            <p>
              The DDEV Foundation is a <a href="/img/blog/2024/03/501c3.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener">US 501(c)(3) non-profit</a>.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <a id="board"></a>
            <h2>Board of Directors</h2>
            <p>
              The DDEV Foundation is governed by a Board of Directors, established to ensure the long-term sustainability and stability of the project. Learn more about this milestone in our <a href="/blog/board-of-directors-established">Board of Directors announcement</a>.
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <img src="/img/blog/2025/12/mike-anello-headshot.jpg" alt="Mike Anello headshot" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Michael Anello</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="https://github.com/ultimike" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@ultimike</a></p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-2">Seasoned Drupal developer with over 15 years of experience. Specializes in Drupal consulting and training, and serves as the Foundation's Treasurer.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <img src="/img/blog/2025/12/jen-lampton-headshot.png" alt="Jen Lampton headshot" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Jen Lampton</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="https://github.com/jenlampton" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@jenlampton</a></p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-2">Building websites since 1997. Co-founder of Backdrop CMS, provisional member of the Drupal security team, and maintains dozens of Open Source projects.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <img src="/img/blog/2025/12/benni-mack-headshot.png" alt="Benni Mack headshot" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Benni Mack</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="https://github.com/bmack" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@bmack</a></p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-2">Long-time TYPO3 core developer and CMS Team Lead. Brings extensive experience in open source project governance and community building.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <img src="/img/blog/2025/12/andrew-berry-headshot.jpg" alt="Andrew Berry headshot" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Andrew Berry</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="https://github.com/deviantintegral" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@deviantintegral</a></p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-2">Member and contributor in the Drupal community since 2006. VP of Technology at Lullabot, where teams rely on DDEV for local development.</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <img src="/img/blog/2025/12/randy-fay-headshot.jpg" alt="Randy Fay headshot" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0" />
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Randy Fay</h3>
                  <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><a href="https://github.com/rfay" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@rfay</a></p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-2">Original maintainer of DDEV since 2016. Deep roots in the Drupal community with a passion for bicycle travel.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2>Where does the money go?</h2>
            <p>
              DDEV Foundation funds are used for infrastructure costs and to pay part-time and full-time maintainers.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2>Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">Contact <a href=/contact>support</a>.</p>
            
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Postal Address & Phone</h3>
            <address class="not-italic">
              {ORG_NAME}<br />
              {ORG_STREET}<br />
              {ORG_CITY}, {ORG_STATE_ABBR} {ORG_POSTAL_CODE} {ORG_COUNTRY}<br />
              <a href={`tel:${ORG_PHONE}`}>{ORG_PHONE}</a>
            </address>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2>Legal Registration and Articles of Incorporation</h2>
            <ul>
              <li>Review our <a href="https://www.sos.state.co.us/biz/BusinessEntityDetail.do?quitButtonDestination=BusinessEntityResults&nameTyp=ENT&masterFileId=20211820326&entityId2=20211820326&fileId=20211820326&srchTyp=ENTITY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Colorado nonprofit corporation registration</a>.</li>
              <li>Our <a href="https://www.sos.state.co.us/biz/ViewImage.do?masterFileId=20211820326&fileId=20258242147">Articles of Incorporation</a> are posted with the State of Colorado, USA.</li>
              <li>US 501(c)(3) nonprofit information available at <a href="https://apps.irs.gov/app/eos/">IRS Tax Exempt Organization Search</a>, search for "DDEV Foundation".</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        </article>
      </PostBody>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
